snippet.title: Sonic 3 & Knuckles - Battle Race - Mini Games
snippet.description:
Sonic 3 & Knuckles - Battle Race is a hack by MarkeyJester and Natsumi which allows 2 players to decide who is a better Sonic the Hedgehog player in a very impressive multiplayer versus competition expirience.

Zenon is Sonic the Hedgehog.
Razor is Miles "Tails" Prower.

Download: http://mrjester.hapisan.com/S3KBR

Join our Discord server: https://dc.railgun.works/qjat5kefvo

#SonicHack
